These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, japanese, dutch, canadian
1. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the argentine##6
3. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the dutch##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the argentine##1
6. the argentine is not the person drinking mirinda##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water    | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | canadian | argentine | dutch | japanese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
City: rome, prague, liverpool, san-francisco
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
4. the person traveling to prague is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
8. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to rome##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | prague  | liverpool    | rome | san-francisco    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, november, july
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, electrician, police-officer
1. the person who's birthday is in july is not the coach##6
2. the doctor is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
3. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
4. the doctor is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the doctor##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
7. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
8. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | july       | december  | june  | november |
| Job        | electrician | police-officer | doctor | coach  |

