.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, ice-hockey, badminton, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, car, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
3. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
5. the person driving the bike is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
7. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | water-polo        | skiing | badminton | ice-hockey |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike | boat     | car   |

