.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, rat, hedgehog, hamster
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the hamster is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the owner of the hedgehog is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
8. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | rat | hedgehog    | horse  | hamster   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

