.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, soy-milk, tea
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, mauve, red, fuchsia
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
7. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
8. the person drinking milk is not the person who likes fuchsia##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | milk  | 7up        | soy-milk      | tea          |
| Job        | light-blue | mauve | fuchsia | red |

