.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, trance, electronic, country
1. the fan jazz is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the fan country is the fan country##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the fan country##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is not the fan country##6
6. the fan trance is not the owner of the fish##6
7. the fan country is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the hedgehog is the fan jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | hedgehog | ferret        | rabbit  | fish     |
| Sport   | jazz     | country | trance | electronic |

