.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, havana, chaman, oliveros
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, time-travel, western
1. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5
2. the havana-smoker is not the person watching romance movies##6
3. the fonseca-smoker is the person watching western movies##1
4. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
5. the fonseca-smoker is between the havana-smoker and the person watching adventure movies##2
6. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | oliveros | havana      | fonseca | chaman   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | time-travel | western   | adventure |

