.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, puzzles, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person drinking water##6
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | water       | hot-chocolate | fanta     | lemonade     |
| Movie-Genre   | camping | puzzles       | board-games | filmmaking |

