1. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | lacrosse | basketball | water-polo | volleyball |
| Transport   | december   | april       | september    | march     |

