.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, apricot, blood-red, chestnut
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who likes orange is not the person who's sport is handball##6
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
8. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | chestnut    | blood-red | apricot | orange         |
| Sport      | handball | lacrosse | golf          | weightlifting |

