1. the person who's hobby is photography is not the montecristo-smoker##6
2. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the ritmeester-smoker##1
6. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
7. the baccarat-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2      |       3       |       4       |
| Hobby   | skydiving  | photography | chess         | rock-climbing |
| Sport   | montecristo | game  | baccarat | ritmeester       |

